      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Our Sincere Apology and Steps to Make Things Right for You\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to personally reach out to you regarding your recent purchase of the espresso machine. I understand how frustrating it must be to have been waiting for your order for two weeks now, and I deeply apologize for the delay caused by an unexpected error at our warehouse. I assure you, it was a genuine mistake made by one of our dedicated team members, and not a result of any computer glitch.\n\nWe truly value your business and are committed to making things right. To express our sincere apologies and make amends, we are offering you a 15% discount on your next order with us. Additionally, we want to ensure you have a positive experience moving forward, so we are also sending you a complimentary gift card for your next purchase as a token of our appreciation.\n\nPlease know that we are taking steps to prevent such errors from happening in the future. We are reviewing our processes and providing additional training to our team to ensure that our customers receive the best service possible.\n\nThank you for your understanding and patience. If you have any further concerns or questions, please do not hesitate to reach out to me",
